column5: I looking to do some ice fishing around the cambridge area like shad's mill, binbrook, or pushlinch whats the bite like and what are you useing write me back.
I've yet to have a bite
got a small pike today at puslinch talked to some other guys they said they got a small one too,lots of cars and sleds out there
what is your target fish??  wolves or panfish???  pm me for info dude.
good plan is to intro yourself and your fav fish species.  welcome aboard bassfromdundas10
well I would like to get into some pike and hopefully get some crappie and thanks
Where in Puslinch do you guys fish?
Slow bite all around is what I'm told but I've only been out once.
